1. *Uplašena* devojčica je panično pokušala da se skloni. (The scared girl tried to flee in panic.)
2. Ogromna oluja je *uplašila* celo selo. (The huge storm scared the entire village.)
3. On joj je rekao da se ne *uplaši*. (He told her not to be afraid.)
4. *Uplašen* policajac je zaustavio automobil. (The scared policeman stopped the car.)
5. Ona je bila *uplašena* od vrele vode. (She was scared of hot water.)